# One-Handed Weapon Tricks
One-Handed Weapons			KEY:Weapon Trick ~ One-Handed Weapons	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Weapon Trick Category.SpecialQuality				ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Weapon Trick ~ Free Hand Maneuver|PRETOTALAB:6	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Weapon Trick ~ Mindful Dodge|PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=FEAT,Dodge	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Weapon Trick ~ Strike and Seize|PREMULT:2,[PRETOTALAB:6],[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=FEAT,Improved Disarm]	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Weapon Trick ~ Stylish Riposte|PREMULT:2,[PRETOTALAB:4],[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=FEAT,Combat Reflexes]

Free Hand Maneuver			KEY:Weapon Trick ~ Free Hand Maneuver	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Weapon Trick.SpecialQuality.One-Handed Weapon Trick	DESC:As a fullround action, you can make a single attack with your weapon and attempt to perform a dirty trickAPG, disarm, dragAPG, repositionAPG, or stealAPG combat maneuver with your free hand, taking no penalties for two-weapon fighting. The combat maneuver provokes attacks of opportunities as normal, unless you have an appropriate ability or feat. You are not considered unarmed for this maneuver, but can't apply any benefits of your weapon to the combat maneuver check.																	SOURCEPAGE:p.8
Mindful Dodge				KEY:Weapon Trick ~ Mindful Dodge		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Weapon Trick.SpecialQuality.One-Handed Weapon Trick	DESC:As an immediate action, you can gain a +4 dodge bonus to your AC against a single of which attack you are aware. You must make this decision before the attack roll is revealed. You are staggered on your next turn.																																																												SOURCEPAGE:p.8
Strike and Seize				KEY:Weapon Trick ~ Strike and Seize		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Weapon Trick.SpecialQuality.One-Handed Weapon Trick	DESC:As a standard action, you can make a single attack with your weapon and attempt to perform a disarm combat maneuver with your free hand, taking no penalties for two-weapon fighting.																																																																	SOURCEPAGE:p.8
Stylish Riposte				KEY:Weapon Trick ~ Stylish Riposte		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Weapon Trick.SpecialQuality.One-Handed Weapon Trick	DESC:When your AC exceeds the result of a foe's melee attack against you by 5 or more, that foe provokes an attack of opportunity from you. Once you make such an attack of opportunity against a foe, you can't again use this trick against the foe that day.																																																						SOURCEPAGE:p.8

# Polearm Tricks
Polearms					KEY:Weapon Trick ~ Polearms			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Weapon Trick Category.SpecialQuality				ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Weapon Trick ~ Choke Up|PRESKILL:2,Acrobatics=1,Climb=1	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Weapon Trick ~ Close Sweep|PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=FEAT,Improved Bull Rush,Improved Reposition,Improved Trip	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Weapon Trick ~ Haft Bash|PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=FEAT,Weapon Focus	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Weapon Trick ~ Polearm Balance|PRESKILL:1,Acrobatics=10	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Weapon Trick ~ Quick Brace|PRETOTALAB:6

Choke Up					KEY:Weapon Trick ~ Choke Up			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Weapon Trick.SpecialQuality.Polearm Trick			DESC:You can take a -2 penalty on attack rolls and damage rolls until the beginning of your next turn in order to choke up on and wield a two-handed polearm sized for you in one hand, as long as you do not make attacks with your other hand.																																																								SOURCEPAGE:p.8
Close Sweep					KEY:Weapon Trick ~ Close Sweep		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Weapon Trick.SpecialQuality.Polearm Trick			DESC:You can attempt a bull rush, repositionAPG, or trip combat maneuver check (one for which you have the matching prerequisite feat) against an adjacent foe, even if wielding a weapon with the reach quality.																																																														SOURCEPAGE:p.8
Haft Bash					KEY:Weapon Trick ~ Haft Bash			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Weapon Trick.SpecialQuality.Polearm Trick			DESC:You can accept a -2 penalty on attack rolls with a reach polearm for which you have Weapon Focus in order to treat the weapon as if it lacked the reach quality until the start of your next turn. If you do, the polearm functions as a club. Any qualities (such as trip) or special abilities (such as keen) of the weapon that a club could not have, and any feats or abilities you can't apply to a club, don't apply to attacks with the weapon during this time.																				SOURCEPAGE:p.8
Polearm Balance				KEY:Weapon Trick ~ Polearm Balance		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Weapon Trick.SpecialQuality.Polearm Trick			DESC:You can use a polearm to improve your balance. Any round in which you do not make a melee attack, you can take 10 on an Acrobatics check even when distraction would normally prevent you from doing so.																																																														SOURCEPAGE:p.8
Quick Brace					KEY:Weapon Trick ~ Quick Brace		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Weapon Trick.SpecialQuality.Polearm Trick			DESC:While taking a fullattack action with a polearm with brace, you can ready an attack with the polearm in place of your final attack. The readied attack uses the attack bonus of the attack you used to ready it.																																																													SOURCEPAGE:p.8

# Ranged Weapon Tricks
Ranged Weapons				KEY:Weapon Trick ~ Ranged Weapons		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Weapon Trick Category.SpecialQuality				ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Weapon Trick ~ Hindering Shot|PREABILITY:2,CATEGORY=FEAT,Precise Shot,Snap Shot	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Weapon Trick ~ Suppressing Shot|PREABILITY:2,CATEGORY=FEAT,Far Shot,Precise Shot

Hindering Shot				KEY:Weapon Trick ~ Hindering Shot		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Weapon Trick.SpecialQuality.Ranged Weapon Trick		DESC:You can distract a foe at a crucial moment, making it vulnerable to your allies' abilities. You can ready an action to make a ranged attack against a foe when an ally forces the foe to attempt a saving throw. If your attack hits the foe and deals damage, the foe takes a -4 penalty on the saving throw that triggered your readied action.																																							SOURCEPAGE:p.8
Suppressing Shot				KEY:Weapon Trick ~ Suppressing Shot		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Weapon Trick.SpecialQuality.Ranged Weapon Trick		DESC:You can cover an ally's momentary vulnerability. You can ready an action to make a ranged attack against a foe when it makes an attack of opportunity. If your attack hits and damages the foe, the foe's attack of opportunity automatically misses its target.																																																					SOURCEPAGE:p.9

