Two-Handed Weapons			KEY:Weapon Trick ~ Two-Handed Weapons	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Weapon Trick Category.SpecialQuality				ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Weapon Trick ~ Cleaving Smash|PREABILITY:3,CATEGORY=FEAT,Cleave,Improved Vital Strike,Power Attack	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Weapon Trick ~ Crush Armor|PREABILITY:2,CATEGORY=FEAT,Improved Sunder,Power Attack	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Weapon Trick ~ Two-Handed Menace|PRESKILL:1,Intimidate=5	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Weapon Trick ~ Warding Weapon|PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=FEAT,Combat Expertise

Cleaving Smash				KEY:Weapon Trick ~ Cleaving Smash		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Weapon Trick.SpecialQuality.Two-Handed Weapon Trick	DESC:When you use Cleave, you can add the additional damage from Vital Strike to both your initial and your secondary attacks. If you also have the Greater Vital Strike feat, you can instead add the damage from Improved Vital Strike to both your initial and your secondary attacks.																																																		SOURCEPAGE:p.9
Crush Armor					KEY:Weapon Trick ~ Crush Armor		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Weapon Trick.SpecialQuality.Two-Handed Weapon Trick	DESC:When you deal damage to a foe's armor with a successful sunder combat maneuver check while using a two-handed weapon, the foe must succeed at a Fortitude save (DC = 10 + 1/2 your base attack bonus + your Strength modifier) or be fatigued for 1 round. If the armor has the broken condition after you damage it, the foe must continue making this save every round until he removes the armor or the armor loses the broken condition. If the armor is destroyed by your sunder attempt, the foe is automatically fatigued for 1 round. The foe cannot become exhausted this way.	SOURCEPAGE:p.9
Two-Handed Menace				KEY:Weapon Trick ~ Two-Handed Menace	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Weapon Trick.SpecialQuality.Two-Handed Weapon Trick	DESC:Capitalizing on the fear inspired by massive weapons, you can take 10 on Intimidate checks even when distracted or in combat.																																																																											SOURCEPAGE:p.9
Warding Weapon				KEY:Weapon Trick ~ Warding Weapon		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Weapon Trick.SpecialQuality.Two-Handed Weapon Trick	DESC:While you are using the total defense action, fighting defensively, or using Combat Expertise, you gain a +1 shield bonus to AC.																																																																										SOURCEPAGE:p.9

# Two-Weapon Tricks
Two Weapons					KEY:Weapon Trick ~ Two Weapons		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Weapon Trick Category.SpecialQuality				ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Weapon Trick ~ Arm Bind|PREABILITY:2,CATEGORY=FEAT,Two-Weapon Defense,Two-Weapon Fighting	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Weapon Trick ~ Dual Strike|PREABILITY:2,CATEGORY=FEAT,Double Slice,Improved Vital Strike	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Weapon Trick ~ Off-Hand Opportunity|PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=FEAT,Combat Reflexes	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Weapon Trick ~ Piercing Climb|PRESKILL:1,Climb=8

Arm Bind					KEY:Weapon Trick ~ Arm Bind			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Weapon Trick.SpecialQuality.Two-Weapon Trick		DESC:You can attempt a combat maneuver check to disarm a foe even if the foe has no weapons. This functions as the disarm combat maneuver. If you succeed and the foe has no weapon, you ensnare an arm of your choice, preventing your foe from using that limb until the end of your next turn. A foe can take a standard action to free its arm.																																								SOURCEPAGE:p.9
Dual Strike					KEY:Weapon Trick ~ Dual Strike		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Weapon Trick.SpecialQuality.Two-Weapon Trick		DESC:As a standard action, you can make two attacks, one with each weapon you're wielding, applying the normal penalties for twoweapon fighting to each.																																																																							SOURCEPAGE:p.9
Off-Hand Opportunity			KEY:Weapon Trick ~ Off-Hand Opportunity	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Weapon Trick.SpecialQuality.Two-Weapon Trick		DESC:You can make one additional attack of opportunity each round with your off-hand weapon.																																																																																	SOURCEPAGE:p.9
Piercing Climb				KEY:Weapon Trick ~ Piercing Climb		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Weapon Trick.SpecialQuality.Two-Weapon Trick		DESC:You can use piercing weapons to climb as if your hands were free. You take a -4 penalty on Stealth checks while doing so. You can take 10 on such Climb checks even while distracted or endangered.																																																															SOURCEPAGE:p.9

